Revision history for Net-Blossom-Server-Backend-S3

0.001000  2026-07-14
    - Initial CPAN release.
    - Store blob bytes in S3-compatible object storage with multipart uploads
      and bounded range downloads.
    - Coordinate object bytes with any Net::Blossom::Server metadata store.
    - Test the live S3 path with three-node Garage and Ceph clusters using
      SQLite and Postgres metadata.
    - Test independent server nodes against shared metadata and object storage.
